reviews.text: Little side corner McDonald’s in City One plaza shopping center. Found some black mold on drop down ceiling tiles above  near return air vent. The ceiling must have leaked and have water stains plus the high humidity hot weather can cause the molding appear. Food is good but needs major attention on surroundings

I ordered a breakfast at 6:30am, on June 20, 2019, restaurant has only one staff working. Do not have menu show up and have to order on Self-ordering machine, can’t get coffee selection. Went to counter, staff is not polite, gave me coffee that is not my choice I said I want black coffee and white coffee she is unpleasantly told me that I have to tell her my coffee preferences, if I can’t do my selection on the machine. She is unwilling to change but after I insist, she then serve the next person, and I have to wait after she finished the customer behind me. She is so unprofessional. Gave one star on this McDonald.
Standard McDonald's, relatively clean with helpful staff
